This Paraphrase on the Romans was executed at Antwerp, probably in May and June 1517 (Ep. 684. 133 cf. Lond. xxiii. 6, LB. 650, 764 Α). The printing began in Oct. (Ep. 687. 15; cf. Ep. 732) and was nearly completed by 21 Nov. (Ep. 719); and by 30 Nov. Erasmus had begun to distribute it to his friends (Ep. 726).
